window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Detective Hydessa Darling has grown up following in her mother's footsteps, always feeling like she is in the shadows of those around her.</b></p> <p>Her mother is infamous for her affinity for murderers and their victims, and she didn't raise her daughters with delusions of how the world truly is.</p> <p>When Hydessa stumbles across a blog describing what could only be a series of murders, she feels drawn to investigate them. But when the identity of the blogger evades them, she must travel undercover to a tourist island hotspot to find out the truth behind the blog and catch the mystery killer.</p> <p>Not everything is what it seems, and soon, Hydessa is entangled in her own dangerous game. Is it a game she can win? Or has she lost before she even arrived on the island?</p> <p><b><i>T</i></b><b> </b> <i>his is a why-choose, MFM, dark contemporary romance. It contains explicit, mature content. The male leads are not prince charmings; they are villains with psycho tendencies. There is stalking, obsessive and possessive behavior, unaliving people, and lots of dark and twisted content. Proceed at your own risk—if you dare.</i></p>"; 
